# Resource-level: Instructors can only view their own session reports

### Test 21: Get Instructor Sessions Report as Admin (Success)
# Replace instructorId with actual instructor ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/instructor-sessions/1?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Test 22: Get Instructor Sessions Report as Instructor (Success - Own Report)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/instructor-sessions/1?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{instructorToken}}

###

### Test 23: Get Instructor Sessions Report - Forbidden (Student)
# Expected: 403 Forbidden
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/instructor-sessions/1?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

###

### Test 24: Get Instructor Sessions Report - Forbidden (Instructor viewing another instructor's report)
# Expected: 403 Forbidden
# Replace instructorId with a different instructor's ID
