Authorization: Bearer {{instructorToken}}

###

### Test 25: Get Instructor Sessions Report - Non-existent Instructor
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/instructor-sessions/999999?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Test 26: Get Instructor Sessions Report - Unauthorized (No token)
# Expected: 401 Unauthorized
