# ===== DATE FILTER TESTS =====

### Test 27: Class Attendance Report - Date Range Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/class-attendance/1?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Test 28: Instructor Sessions Report - Date Range Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/instructor-sessions/1?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

