### Test 29: Attendance Summary - Invalid Date Range (Bad Request)
# Expected: 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/attendance-summary?startDate=2024-12-31&endDate=2024-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

# ===== AUTHORIZATION WORKFLOW TESTS =====
# These tests verify the resource-level authorization we implemented

### Test 30: Cross-Instructor Access Test - Class Attendance
# Instructor A tries to view Instructor B's section
# Expected: 403 Forbidden
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/class-attendance/2?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{instructorToken}}

###

### Test 31: Cross-Instructor Access Test - Instructor Sessions
# Instructor A tries to view Instructor B's session report
# Expected: 403 Forbidden
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/instructor-sessions/2?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{instructorToken}}

###

### Test 32: Admin Can Access Everything
# Admin should be able to access any report regardless of ownership
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/class-attendance/2?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/instructor-sessions/2?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

